FILE DESCRIPTIONS
• /assets/css/styles.css → Styles for the UI.
• /assets/js/script.js → JavaScript for interactivity.
• /includes/db_connect.php → Database connection file.
• /includes/header.php → Header section.
• /includes/footer.php → Footer section.
• /includes/navbar.php → Navigation bar.
• /auth/login.php → User login page.
• /auth/register.php → User registration page.
• /auth/logout.php → Destroys session and logs out user.
• /pages/dashboard.php → Main admin panel.
• /pages/orders.php → Manage orders (View, Update, Delete).
• /pages/add_order.php → Create new orders.
• /pages/inventory.php → Manage product inventory.
• /pages/suppliers.php → Supplier management.
• /pages/analytics.php → Profit margin and sales tracking.
• /pages/profile.php → User profile and settings.
• /crud/ → Contains PHP scripts for CRUD operations.
• /database/init_db.sql → SQL script to set up the database.
• /config.php → Configuration file for global settings.
• /index.php → Homepage.
